RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2009-2310. Dialysis Clinic, Inc. v. Levin.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2006-V-2389. Reported at 127 Ohio St.3d 215, 2010-Ohio-5071, 938 N.E.2d *1487329. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied. Motion to strike denied as moot.

Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent.
